---
title: Mexican Quinoa
servings: 4
tags:
  - entres
---

Cook @quinoa{1%cup}(uncooked) and @black beans{1.5%cup}(cooked, if needed).

Add the quinoa, black beans, @diced tomatoes{14%oz}(canned), @bell peppers{3}, @garlic{4%cloves}, @small onion{1}, @oil{}, @broth{1%cup}, @chili powder{}, and @cumin powder{} to a #pot{}, bring to a boil, and simmer for ~{20%minutes}.

Garnish with @avocado{}, @lime{}, and @cilantro{} before serving.
